Package: tidyjaccard
Title: Effortlessly Compute Pairwise Jaccard Similarity from Tidy Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "El-Kamand", , "sam.elkamand@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2270-8088"))
Description: Provides an intuitive way to compute pairwise Jaccard similarity from tidy datasets. Given a dataframe with unique sample identifiers and sets of elements per sample, this package calculates Jaccard similarity and returns the mapping in a tidy dataframe.
